tags: Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Doctor friendliness,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
It's highly essential to explain concerned problem and best possible solution of that particular problem.

In my case, I was explained my tooth problem in simple layman's language and best possible solution of Dental Implant was suggested by Dr. Prasad Rane.

Also, when I asked about the cist of implant, he explained me that Dental Implant starts from 28,000/- and also explained me that he can let me know about exact cost of Implant only after the tooth scan.

I got satisfaction in the first visit itself and today I have a followup at Doctor's Dental Clinic.

The clinic is 5 minutes from my residence and this is added benefit.

I highly recommend Dr. Prasad Rane. Please visit his Dental Clinic and get best treatment.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: I have been having a great relation with Dr. Prasad Rane at My Smile Dental clinic for almost 8 years now. I have had my root canal treatments, wisdom tooth extractions, dental fillings and teeth cleaning with polishing done at his clinic. Amazingly, he seems to always have all my necessary dental records - big or small, that he has performed on me since the very beginning. That way he has access to my dental history at his fingertips. He makes me feel relaxed and worry free and all of the above mentioned procedures have been super comfortable and almost pain-free for me. He has been upgrading himself with changing times and has all the advanced tools and machines The clinic is always hygienic following covid protocols with a welcoming and friendly staff.

review: *** ****** **** ** ******** *** **** ******* ** *** ****** It's not just his craft he is fabulous at, it's his charm, his communication, his care and his counsel. From making a patient feel absolutely at ease with an assurance that nothing can be too bad, that everything has a solution to the execution of his schedule, he and his team are incomparable. I have reason to believe he has wizard hands... I got some elaborate work done at his clinic without an iota of pain or discomfort. Instead, he made it feel like home, right down to the music that he plays as he works his magic! His setup is spick and span with all measures and protocol of safety and hygiene in place. His equipment and technology seem to the finest I have known or seen. His team is extremely cooperative and courteous. They will always meet you with a solution and a smile :)

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
Dr. Prasad Rane’s approach is very comforting. His treatment philosophy always is “let’s retain the natural tooth as much as we can”. I went to him for a second opinion for a root canal therapy and after thorough evaluation and weighing all options, based on his suggestion I went for filling as the cavity exposure to root was very minimal. He was honest that “the filling may fail, but it is worth giving a shot as it would help retain the natural tooth”. Went for filling and no problem even after an year. Now Dr. Prasad is favourite dentist of my daughter too. She says “even after growing up, where ever I am, if I have to go to a dentist, I will go to Dr. Prasad only” :)
His clinic is very clean and well equipped and his staff are also very courteous and helpful.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Wait time,
review:
****** ** **** *************, witty, smart and at the same time patient-friendly and down to earth. He clearly assesses the problem statement and then provides the best solution available while giving pros and cons of alternate treatments. This helps the patient to build confidence in the treatment.
Dr is very polite and generous person. He'll take every effort to explain the root cause, treatment and post treatment precaution. He's never in a hurry to rush appointments. 
The clinic is very clean with utmost levels of hygiene maintained. The helping staff is also very courteous, well trained and professional.
I visited for my grandmother's(82yrs) denture. Since the doctor is also a professor he sought the best available option to provide her the best type of fixture. As of a week now after using the new set of dentures, she's very satisfied with the overall procedure.
I'll definitely REFER & RECOMMEND Dr for a 100% satisfactory dental treatment
